1
00:01:28,940 --> 00:01:35,460
Winter Begonia

2
00:01:35,460 --> 00:01:37,940
Episode 15

3
00:01:41,780 --> 00:01:44,280
Have your Head Gu come talk to me!

4
00:01:45,060 --> 00:01:48,490
Cheng Fengtai, let me tell you.

5
00:01:49,530 --> 00:01:53,729
There… there’s no such person anymore.

6
00:01:55,410 --> 00:02:00,690
From now on, I’m the boss.

7
00:02:02,530 --> 00:02:06,230
I’ve… I’ve just got rid of…

8
00:02:07,120 --> 00:02:08,650
Got rid of Head Gu?

9
00:02:09,320 --> 00:02:11,020
Yes, I did.

10
00:02:12,260 --> 00:02:14,690
But Gu Dali, that chick…

11
00:02:14,700 --> 00:02:17,920
She… she got… got away.

12
00:02:19,940 --> 00:02:20,670
But it’s fine.

13
00:02:21,790 --> 00:02:24,260
You brought me the

14
00:02:24,270 --> 00:02:26,140
arms and ammunition today.

15
00:02:26,600 --> 00:02:30,090
We’re all set here.

16
00:02:30,410 --> 00:02:32,370
I… I’m not afraid.

17
00:02:32,610 --> 00:02:34,380
Aren’t you afraid of Gu Dali coming back?

18
00:02:36,380 --> 00:02:37,010
Right.

19
00:02:37,340 --> 00:02:38,850
You’ve got the guns and the men now.

20
00:02:39,200 --> 00:02:40,320
Of course you’re not afraid.

21
00:02:40,660 --> 00:02:41,870
Shut up!

22
00:02:45,230 --> 00:02:46,960
What’s there… there… to…

23
00:02:47,100 --> 00:02:48,860
to be afraid of….

24
00:02:49,640 --> 00:02:51,240
Shut your mouth.

25
00:02:54,560 --> 00:02:55,640
You have the guns now.

26
00:02:56,440 --> 00:02:57,500
Let them go.

27
00:02:57,510 --> 00:02:58,170
No way.

28
00:02:59,160 --> 00:03:00,010
Let me tell you.

29
00:03:00,560 --> 00:03:02,350
Someone wants you dead.

30
00:03:02,360 --> 00:03:04,080
You won’t be able to leave.

31
00:03:06,550 --> 00:03:08,250
A lot of people want me dead.

32
00:03:08,950 --> 00:03:10,640
Which one are you talking about?

33
00:03:10,830 --> 00:03:13,040
I’ll see if I really can’t leave for myself.

34
00:03:14,970 --> 00:03:16,810
You’ve got balls.

35
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:18,290
Seemingly you’ll definitely make it out

36
00:03:18,300 --> 00:03:19,370
if I told you.

37
00:03:19,380 --> 00:03:19,980
Boss…

38
00:03:25,390 --> 00:03:26,660
Cheng Fengtai!

39
00:03:27,170 --> 00:03:29,430
How dare you lie to me!

40
00:03:29,440 --> 00:03:31,970
Tell me where the magazine was!

41
00:03:33,079 --> 00:03:33,810
Say it!

42
00:03:35,600 --> 00:03:36,300
The guns…

43
00:03:37,370 --> 00:03:39,920
I took them apart to transport them separately.

44
00:03:40,540 --> 00:03:42,340
Just to be safe on the road.

45
00:03:42,350 --> 00:03:43,120
Or in case anyone wouldn’t pay as agreed.

46
00:03:43,579 --> 00:03:45,700
They can’t do anything with half of a gun.

47
00:03:46,540 --> 00:03:48,320
That’s how we negotiate.

48
00:03:49,420 --> 00:03:51,490
Second Chief Gu, let them go.

49
00:03:52,130 --> 00:03:53,800
I’ll give you

50
00:03:57,010 --> 00:03:58,120
the rest of the magazines.

51
00:03:59,350 --> 00:03:59,820
You!

52
00:04:02,760 --> 00:04:04,130
You bastard…

53
00:04:04,670 --> 00:04:06,690
You’ve got games…

54
00:04:07,770 --> 00:04:09,270
I can just… just…

55
00:04:09,280 --> 00:04:10,320
I… I… I…

56
00:04:10,620 --> 00:04:11,100
I’m going to ….

57
00:04:11,110 --> 00:04:12,360
Boss!

58
00:04:13,760 --> 00:04:14,460
Boss!

59
00:04:17,390 --> 00:04:18,140
Something bad happened.

60
00:04:19,420 --> 00:04:21,930
Gu Dali is coming back for us!

61
00:04:23,570 --> 00:04:25,930
She… she…

62
00:04:26,520 --> 00:04:27,880
she’s looking to be killed.

63
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:29,850
Lock him up!

64
00:04:30,230 --> 00:04:31,520
I’ll deal with you later.

65
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:32,620
Let’s go!

66
00:04:33,030 --> 00:04:33,960
Come on! Now!

67
00:04:33,970 --> 00:04:35,450
Let’s go…

68
00:04:39,220 --> 00:04:54,500
(Master)

69
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:57,170
This Shang Xirui

70
00:04:57,510 --> 00:04:59,250
is really taking his time.

71
00:04:59,260 --> 00:05:02,040
Most of you, sirs, are seniors.

72
00:05:02,650 --> 00:05:04,880
He really doesn’t have any manner.

73
00:05:05,050 --> 00:05:06,320
Agreed.

74
00:05:11,060 --> 00:05:12,070
Let’s see…

75
00:05:21,190 --> 00:05:21,900
Xirui.

76
00:05:24,810 --> 00:05:25,840
Mr. Niu ,

77
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:28,280
what happened to Mr. Jiang?

78
00:05:29,090 --> 00:05:31,160
Something wrong with him?

79
00:05:31,290 --> 00:05:34,100
He had us coming all the way here for nothing?

80
00:05:34,110 --> 00:05:36,430
Mr. Du, what brought you here?

81
00:05:36,440 --> 00:05:37,440
Of course I had to come.

82
00:05:38,130 --> 00:05:40,200
Jiang Rongshou is a monster.

83
00:05:40,380 --> 00:05:41,550
You can’t go against him.

84
00:05:41,810 --> 00:05:44,030
No way. Everyone is watching.

85
00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:45,450
Mr. Jiang cannot be

86
00:05:45,570 --> 00:05:47,200
too ruthless.

87
00:05:47,930 --> 00:05:49,090
I wouldn’t be so sure.

88
00:05:51,140 --> 00:05:51,920
Mr. Niu,

89
00:05:53,890 --> 00:05:57,240
I’m not sure if I should say this…

90
00:05:57,250 --> 00:05:57,820
Please.

91
00:05:58,820 --> 00:06:00,310
People like us, individually,

92
00:06:00,560 --> 00:06:02,980
we all look nice and charming.

93
00:06:02,990 --> 00:06:05,390
But once being in the same room,

94
00:06:05,400 --> 00:06:06,500
all we do is fight.

95
00:06:06,950 --> 00:06:08,350
So many schemes

96
00:06:08,360 --> 00:06:10,230
and conspiracies.

97
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:12,000
Don’t you think it’s a bit pathetic?

98
00:06:12,430 --> 00:06:14,090
Right.

99
00:06:14,100 --> 00:06:15,210
You’re criticising me as well.

100
00:06:17,060 --> 00:06:19,970
But you have a point.

101
00:06:20,520 --> 00:06:21,800
What happened behind the scene,

102
00:06:22,020 --> 00:06:23,000
the other people don’t see it.

103
00:06:23,430 --> 00:06:25,770
Sometimes I feel ashamed as well.

104
00:06:26,120 --> 00:06:27,330
This Mr. Jiang

105
00:06:27,340 --> 00:06:29,140
just can’t stand others doing better than him.

106
00:06:29,690 --> 00:06:31,320
He wants to bring Mr. Shang down.

107
00:06:31,690 --> 00:06:32,659
Let me remind you,

108
00:06:33,210 --> 00:06:36,200
I wrote the new script for Shuiyun Theater.

109
00:06:36,210 --> 00:06:37,630
I own a part of it.

110
00:06:37,790 --> 00:06:39,460
I’ll fight for Xirui.

111
00:06:39,470 --> 00:06:40,220
No, no, no.

112
00:06:40,440 --> 00:06:41,260
Mr. Du.

113
00:06:41,520 --> 00:06:44,200
This could be a very dangerous place.

114
00:06:46,370 --> 00:06:47,920
You think I’m afraid of danger?

115
00:06:48,210 --> 00:06:49,920
Mr. Du,

116
00:06:50,180 --> 00:06:52,480
only successors of Zhang Beidou can go today.

117
00:06:53,570 --> 00:06:54,920
Has to be successors?

118
00:06:55,110 --> 00:06:56,680
Yes. It has to be.

119
00:06:57,180 --> 00:06:57,760
That’s easy.

120
00:07:00,610 --> 00:07:01,560
Master,

121
00:07:02,230 --> 00:07:03,400
please accept me as your apprentice.

122
00:07:04,190 --> 00:07:04,710
Mr. Du.

123
00:07:04,900 --> 00:07:06,040
You’re a Childe.

124
00:07:06,050 --> 00:07:06,890
You can’t do this.

125
00:07:06,900 --> 00:07:07,390
Get up, please.

126
00:07:08,780 --> 00:07:09,370
People!

127
00:07:10,200 --> 00:07:12,050
I, Du Luocheng,

128
00:07:12,400 --> 00:07:15,010
take Shang Xirui as my master.

129
00:07:15,490 --> 00:07:17,930
Everyone shall be my witness today.

130
00:07:22,300 --> 00:07:24,020
Look at him. Doing this in public.

131
00:07:24,680 --> 00:07:25,810
He must really like him.

132
00:07:25,820 --> 00:07:26,440
I know.

133
00:07:26,880 --> 00:07:28,690
So, did he just become Mr. Shang’s apprentice?

134
00:07:30,670 --> 00:07:31,760
We’ll talk about the rules later.

135
00:07:31,770 --> 00:07:33,970
Let’s go visit grandmaster Zhang first.

136
00:07:33,980 --> 00:07:35,030
Yes, master!

137
00:07:35,850 --> 00:07:38,450
Shang Xirui, the fifth generation student of Zhang Beidou.

138
00:07:38,460 --> 00:07:40,420
Du Luocheng, the sixth generation.

139
00:07:40,430 --> 00:07:42,340
We’re here to visit our grandmaster.

140
00:07:44,180 --> 00:07:45,430
Oh, they’re going to see the grandmaster.

141
00:07:45,440 --> 00:07:46,240
Mr. Du,

142
00:07:46,250 --> 00:07:48,080
this is a bad time to fool about!

143
00:07:49,060 --> 00:07:53,620
(Master)

144
00:07:57,940 --> 00:07:58,730
Brother Liu.

145
00:07:59,940 --> 00:08:00,710
Uncle Bai.

146
00:08:01,360 --> 00:08:02,160
Uncle Zhang.

147
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:04,120
Brother Huang.

148
00:08:04,820 --> 00:08:05,540
Uncle Wang.

149
00:08:08,900 --> 00:08:09,690
Chairman Jiang.

150
00:08:23,720 --> 00:08:26,420
Mr. Jiang, Shang Xirui is here.

151
00:08:29,530 --> 00:08:31,250
I’m not deaf.

152
00:08:39,090 --> 00:08:40,870
Today, we’re here to send off

153
00:08:40,880 --> 00:08:42,720
someone who passed away.

154
00:08:44,049 --> 00:08:44,840
Mr. Du,

155
00:08:45,750 --> 00:08:47,580
you should follow Confucius.

156
00:08:48,030 --> 00:08:50,930
We follow the Opera God.

157
00:08:50,940 --> 00:08:52,680
You’re a sophisticated scholar.

158
00:08:52,690 --> 00:08:54,920
You shouldn’t be at such a place.

159
00:08:55,270 --> 00:08:56,320
Throughout the history,

160
00:08:57,260 --> 00:09:00,160
the best scholars always write scripts.

161
00:09:01,580 --> 00:09:03,470
I write plays for Mr. Shang.

162
00:09:04,540 --> 00:09:06,260
Shouldn’t that make me

163
00:09:07,790 --> 00:09:09,700
a part of the opera industry?

164
00:09:10,360 --> 00:09:12,160
What’s more,

165
00:09:13,770 --> 00:09:15,600
I’ve just asked Mr. Shang to be my master.

166
00:09:16,430 --> 00:09:19,400
Coming here today to pay my respect to the grandmaster

167
00:09:19,940 --> 00:09:22,230
is my responsibility.

168
00:09:25,620 --> 00:09:28,190
I respect grandmaster Zhang a lot.

169
00:09:28,910 --> 00:09:31,910
Gentlemen, I hope you don’t mind me paying my respect now.

170
00:09:33,820 --> 00:09:35,010
When did they do that?

171
00:09:48,090 --> 00:09:48,720
Sir,

172
00:09:48,990 --> 00:09:50,980
let’s put the incense up.

173
00:09:50,990 --> 00:09:52,640
We have to prepare for the show.

174
00:09:55,300 --> 00:09:58,180
Mr. Du knows how to protect someone.

175
00:09:59,340 --> 00:10:01,650
Shang Xirui is an upright man.

176
00:10:02,060 --> 00:10:03,630
I don’t need to protect him.

177
00:10:04,170 --> 00:10:05,300
Even if I do,

178
00:10:05,710 --> 00:10:07,930
it’s a student’s responsibility

179
00:10:08,490 --> 00:10:10,080
to protect his master.

180
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:12,420
Protect him…

181
00:10:14,130 --> 00:10:14,940
Well, if he had done

182
00:10:14,950 --> 00:10:16,720
something bad,

183
00:10:17,000 --> 00:10:18,940
no one can protect him.

184
00:10:22,630 --> 00:10:23,370
Sir,

185
00:10:24,320 --> 00:10:25,600
funny thing you said.

186
00:10:26,260 --> 00:10:28,320
Mr. Shang focuses only on operas.

187
00:10:29,090 --> 00:10:30,440
What did he do?

188
00:10:34,190 --> 00:10:36,410
If there’s anything,

189
00:10:37,850 --> 00:10:40,820
it must the competition between Shuiyun and Longchun.

190
00:10:40,830 --> 00:10:42,790
Longchun Troupe lost its business

191
00:10:42,800 --> 00:10:43,520
and its audience.

192
00:10:44,380 --> 00:10:46,900
Are you trying to protect Longchun Troupe?

193
00:10:48,090 --> 00:10:49,760
Mr. Du, that’s enough.

194
00:10:49,770 --> 00:10:52,430
I think, performers

195
00:10:52,440 --> 00:10:54,030
should focus on performing.

196
00:10:54,040 --> 00:10:55,900
Instead of playing tricks here and there.

197
00:10:55,910 --> 00:10:57,360
This should be your priority.

198
00:10:58,370 --> 00:11:00,190
Don’t you agree?

199
00:11:04,830 --> 00:11:08,940
Your father did write many great scripts.

200
00:11:09,230 --> 00:11:12,390
And all of us artists appreciate it.

201
00:11:12,620 --> 00:11:15,250
But even your father

202
00:11:15,380 --> 00:11:16,130
would just respect me

203
00:11:16,140 --> 00:11:19,130
in front of our grandmaster.

204
00:11:20,370 --> 00:11:23,020
Your scripts are outrageous.

205
00:11:23,660 --> 00:11:26,620
Only Shang Xirui appreciates it.

206
00:11:27,680 --> 00:11:30,340
With all due respect,

207
00:11:30,350 --> 00:11:32,380
Mr. Du, we will take care of our own business.

208
00:11:32,890 --> 00:11:34,190
We’d hate to trouble you.

209
00:11:34,200 --> 00:11:35,230
See him out.

210
00:11:35,240 --> 00:11:37,840
Mr. Du, the gate is that way.

211
00:11:37,850 --> 00:11:38,790
Please.

212
00:11:44,060 --> 00:11:46,110
I’ve said what I said anyways.

213
00:11:47,650 --> 00:11:48,820
I’ll take the opportunity

214
00:11:49,290 --> 00:11:51,160
to tell all the gentlemen here today:

215
00:11:51,770 --> 00:11:52,720
it’s a shame that

216
00:11:53,060 --> 00:11:54,920
I have been fairly useless for 20 years.

217
00:11:55,060 --> 00:11:56,440
I didn’t achieve much academically.

218
00:11:56,780 --> 00:11:59,050
Surely you can’t compare me with my father.

219
00:12:03,680 --> 00:12:05,200
If I hadn’t met Shang Xirui,

220
00:12:06,120 --> 00:12:08,080
I would’ve never started to write.

221
00:12:09,840 --> 00:12:11,280
Now that I’ve met him,

222
00:12:12,040 --> 00:12:13,170
I don’t ever

223
00:12:13,450 --> 00:12:15,400
need to write for anyone else.

224
00:12:16,060 --> 00:12:18,630
No one else can bring my scripts to life.

225
00:12:18,920 --> 00:12:20,490
No one can do it justice.

226
00:12:22,110 --> 00:12:24,260
Are you out of your mind, Mr. Du?

227
00:12:24,620 --> 00:12:25,830
Are you serious?

228
00:12:25,840 --> 00:12:27,580
No artist can do your scripts justice?

229
00:12:27,590 --> 00:12:29,680
Only Mr. Shang can?

230
00:12:29,690 --> 00:12:31,240
I’ll have to see if our grandmaster

231
00:12:31,250 --> 00:12:32,400
agree or not.

232
00:12:32,690 --> 00:12:35,540
Mr. Shang risked everything.

233
00:12:35,550 --> 00:12:36,470
He wasn’t afraid of being taken down

234
00:12:36,480 --> 00:12:37,910
or ruining his reputation.

235
00:12:37,920 --> 00:12:39,260
He insisted on using my script.

236
00:12:39,450 --> 00:12:41,290
He shouldered all the criticism and insults,

237
00:12:41,300 --> 00:12:42,890
until the audience started to love it.

238
00:12:43,230 --> 00:12:44,130
That’s how you, gentlemen,

239
00:12:44,140 --> 00:12:46,860
found out about me.

240
00:12:47,190 --> 00:12:48,190
Let me ask you,

241
00:12:48,200 --> 00:12:49,640
gentlemen,

242
00:12:50,320 --> 00:12:52,530
if I hadn’t met Shang Xirui,

243
00:12:52,940 --> 00:12:54,690
if I had come to you with my script

244
00:12:54,700 --> 00:12:57,400
asking you to take it,

245
00:12:57,790 --> 00:12:59,360
would you have taken it?

246
00:13:08,800 --> 00:13:09,810
Of course!

247
00:13:10,740 --> 00:13:12,770
Why wouldn’t we?

248
00:13:13,000 --> 00:13:14,080
You don’t deserve it.

249
00:13:16,010 --> 00:13:17,120
From now on,

250
00:13:17,130 --> 00:13:19,410
I will only write for Mr. Shang.

251
00:13:19,420 --> 00:13:21,340
He’ll be the only person who is allowed to use it.

252
00:13:21,540 --> 00:13:22,920
If he isn’t the one who performs,

253
00:13:23,060 --> 00:13:24,340
I simply can’t pick up the pen.

254
00:13:24,670 --> 00:13:25,440
Any problem

255
00:13:25,560 --> 00:13:27,060
you have in the future,

256
00:13:27,070 --> 00:13:28,570
feel free to come to me.

257
00:13:29,520 --> 00:13:30,680
If I see anyone

258
00:13:30,690 --> 00:13:32,420
try to insult him

259
00:13:32,610 --> 00:13:33,480
or spread rumors about him,

260
00:13:33,730 --> 00:13:36,080
I will not think twice to cut you off.

261
00:13:37,330 --> 00:13:41,120
You said you took him as your master.

262
00:13:42,330 --> 00:13:44,480
Did Du Hanlin give you the approval?

263
00:13:46,930 --> 00:13:47,960
My father can’t stop me.

264
00:13:48,210 --> 00:13:50,500
Mr. Du hasn’t go home in a while, right?

265
00:13:50,510 --> 00:13:52,820
Always writing at the Liuguo Hotel.

266
00:13:52,830 --> 00:13:54,480
None of your business.

267
00:13:57,000 --> 00:13:58,990
Your father hasn’t left his bed

268
00:13:59,000 --> 00:14:00,920
the entire winter.

269
00:14:01,040 --> 00:14:02,000
You’re not aware of it?

270
00:14:03,580 --> 00:14:07,420
Is Shang Xirui more important than your own father?

271
00:14:07,960 --> 00:14:09,390
It’s okay, you didn’t know.

272
00:14:10,020 --> 00:14:11,020
But now you do.

273
00:14:11,030 --> 00:14:12,510
Shouldn’t you go home and see him?

274
00:14:12,680 --> 00:14:15,960
Don’t be a heartless son.

275
00:14:15,970 --> 00:14:17,370
You idiot.

276
00:14:19,820 --> 00:14:20,730
That’s enough help for today.

277
00:14:21,360 --> 00:14:21,780
That’s okay.

278
00:14:22,680 --> 00:14:23,160
Go home.

279
00:14:23,520 --> 00:14:24,600
Yes, Mr. Du.

280
00:14:24,800 --> 00:14:25,500
I’ll stay and help him.

281
00:14:26,070 --> 00:14:26,910
Don’t worry.

282
00:14:26,920 --> 00:14:28,340
Go home and see your father.

283
00:14:29,280 --> 00:14:29,720
Let’s go.

284
00:14:30,580 --> 00:14:31,650
Mr. Du.

285
00:14:32,100 --> 00:14:33,100
What are you waiting for?

286
00:14:33,250 --> 00:14:34,360
Please.

287
00:14:35,370 --> 00:14:36,410
It’s okay. It’s fine.

288
00:14:38,320 --> 00:14:39,580
Let’s go. Let’s go.

289
00:14:39,990 --> 00:14:40,830
That’s enough.

290
00:14:44,910 --> 00:14:47,470
You disrespectful little bastard.

291
00:14:48,870 --> 00:14:52,350
You should apologise to your grandmaster on your knees now.

292
00:15:30,220 --> 00:15:31,000
Brother,

293
00:15:32,070 --> 00:15:32,960
you’re here.

294
00:15:33,760 --> 00:15:36,080
Still resting so well, even in here.

295
00:15:36,280 --> 00:15:37,550
Quite adapting.

296
00:15:44,470 --> 00:15:45,970
How can I not be?

297
00:15:48,120 --> 00:15:49,890
I count my days all the time.

298
00:15:50,450 --> 00:15:52,020
Hoping you would show up

299
00:15:52,030 --> 00:15:53,000
and save me from hell.

300
00:15:54,720 --> 00:15:55,610
Who knew

301
00:15:56,860 --> 00:15:58,380
all I got was another roommate.

302
00:15:59,230 --> 00:16:01,360
I’m trying to use my wisdom

303
00:16:01,370 --> 00:16:02,230
to save you from this.

304
00:16:02,990 --> 00:16:05,060
But just when I was trying,

305
00:16:05,340 --> 00:16:07,620
some help just showed up and stopped me.

306
00:16:08,630 --> 00:16:11,110
Are you saying someone is coming to get us?

307
00:16:38,100 --> 00:16:38,900
Chief,

308
00:16:39,590 --> 00:16:41,240
Erjieba’s people can’t stop us now.

309
00:16:42,520 --> 00:16:43,460
Laozi Ridge

310
00:16:43,940 --> 00:16:46,210
was left for me by my father.

311
00:16:48,070 --> 00:16:48,820
This Second Chief Gu,

312
00:16:49,250 --> 00:16:50,760
disrespected my father and killed him.

313
00:16:50,770 --> 00:16:52,610
Now he’s trying to take the Ridge away from me.

314
00:16:53,160 --> 00:16:54,060
Brothers,

315
00:16:54,330 --> 00:16:55,440
attack!

316
00:16:55,610 --> 00:16:57,030
For my father!

317
00:16:57,040 --> 00:16:58,310
Revenge!

318
00:16:58,320 --> 00:16:59,990
- Go! - Go!

319
00:17:01,620 --> 00:17:03,140
Can Mr. Jiang enlighten me,

320
00:17:04,130 --> 00:17:06,010
when did I disrespect anyone?

321
00:17:12,480 --> 00:17:15,050
Tell me what this is.

322
00:17:17,970 --> 00:17:18,650
Look at it.

323
00:17:21,230 --> 00:17:22,839
Gentlemen, take a good look.

324
00:17:23,630 --> 00:17:24,640
Have you seen such thing before?

325
00:17:25,339 --> 00:17:26,690
Have you?

326
00:17:26,960 --> 00:17:27,880
I bet none of you

327
00:17:27,890 --> 00:17:29,700
can even imagine such thing exists.

328
00:17:30,370 --> 00:17:31,790
Awfully strange, right?

329
00:17:31,950 --> 00:17:33,050
Outrageous.

330
00:17:33,940 --> 00:17:35,660
I’d like to ask Shang Xirui.

331
00:17:36,560 --> 00:17:38,420
Was this something from our grandmaster?

332
00:17:38,800 --> 00:17:41,640
Or did you create this?

333
00:17:42,400 --> 00:17:43,810
As far as I’m concerned,

334
00:17:43,820 --> 00:17:45,960
Mr. Shang’s shows are just fine.

335
00:17:46,840 --> 00:17:49,160
Haven’t you seen these modern shows and films?

336
00:17:49,760 --> 00:17:51,310
Kissing, hugging and showing flesh…

337
00:17:51,320 --> 00:17:52,140
They do everything.

338
00:17:52,600 --> 00:17:54,480
It’s about time

339
00:17:54,490 --> 00:17:55,300
for us to progress

340
00:17:55,310 --> 00:17:56,470
with our opera costumes.

341
00:17:56,680 --> 00:17:58,240
Wouldn’t it be progressive?

342
00:17:58,440 --> 00:18:00,370
Don’t talk to me about modern shows.

343
00:18:01,240 --> 00:18:03,550
Those hairy white people.

344
00:18:03,880 --> 00:18:07,360
You can’t compare them with Beijing Opera artists.

345
00:18:08,310 --> 00:18:10,120
The traditional roles

346
00:18:10,240 --> 00:18:11,830
are not traditional anymore.

347
00:18:11,840 --> 00:18:13,590
All these modern stuff.

348
00:18:13,720 --> 00:18:16,020
Our ancestors left us with treasure.

349
00:18:16,370 --> 00:18:18,130
He’s ruined it.

350
00:18:18,780 --> 00:18:21,490
Mr. Shang’s Zhao Feiyan is competing against mine.

351
00:18:22,110 --> 00:18:23,320
Shouldn’t I be the one

352
00:18:23,330 --> 00:18:24,400
to approve costumes?

353
00:18:24,800 --> 00:18:25,970
Hear ye hear ye!

354
00:18:26,460 --> 00:18:28,390
Mr. Chen should have the authority.

355
00:18:28,940 --> 00:18:29,880
Look at it.

356
00:18:29,890 --> 00:18:30,880
Look at what he’s done

357
00:18:30,890 --> 00:18:31,700
to defeat you.

358
00:18:43,550 --> 00:18:45,660
Grandmaster,

359
00:18:46,640 --> 00:18:50,530
this costume is extremely strange.

360
00:18:50,920 --> 00:18:52,950
Not long enough.

361
00:18:53,440 --> 00:18:55,960
Not short enough.

362
00:18:56,200 --> 00:18:58,600
Tight at the top

363
00:18:58,890 --> 00:19:01,610
and loose in the bottom.

364
00:19:02,400 --> 00:19:04,930
Indeed.

365
00:19:05,500 --> 00:19:06,770
It doesn’t meet the standard.

366
00:19:07,330 --> 00:19:09,420
But we also can’t deny

367
00:19:10,090 --> 00:19:12,220
that it is innovative.

368
00:19:14,990 --> 00:19:17,090
What are you talking about?

369
00:19:18,650 --> 00:19:19,610
What is it?

370
00:19:23,260 --> 00:19:25,050
You claimed to be right.

371
00:19:25,780 --> 00:19:27,960
He claimed to be right.

372
00:19:28,960 --> 00:19:30,840
Who is right?

373
00:19:31,850 --> 00:19:33,650
Only God knows.

374
00:19:33,960 --> 00:19:34,970
Unbelievable.

375
00:19:36,260 --> 00:19:37,280
Get out of here.

376
00:19:37,640 --> 00:19:38,170
That’s enough.

377
00:19:41,700 --> 00:19:42,880
He’s too young…

378
00:19:44,090 --> 00:19:44,780
Alright.

379
00:19:46,530 --> 00:19:47,450
Shang Xirui.

380
00:19:47,680 --> 00:19:49,130
Explain for yourself.

381
00:19:50,050 --> 00:19:51,650
What is this thing here?

382
00:19:55,020 --> 00:19:57,200
Can I ask you to fold it

383
00:19:57,210 --> 00:19:58,400
and put it back in the case?

384
00:19:58,950 --> 00:19:59,710
They’re precious to me.

385
00:20:07,220 --> 00:20:08,810
Let’s not talk about

386
00:20:08,820 --> 00:20:10,430
how you got my costumes for now.

387
00:20:11,240 --> 00:20:12,480
I designed

388
00:20:13,350 --> 00:20:15,420
this costume based on the painting on Buddhist scriptures.

389
00:20:16,330 --> 00:20:18,800
These scriptures are older than this art itself.

390
00:20:19,780 --> 00:20:21,480
This is how they dress in the past.

391
00:20:22,690 --> 00:20:25,250
Zhao Feiyan is a concubine from Han dynasty.

392
00:20:25,560 --> 00:20:27,000
Why shouldn’t I wear it?

393
00:20:27,610 --> 00:20:29,040
I didn’t change anything.

394
00:20:29,640 --> 00:20:30,900
If you don’t believe me,

395
00:20:30,910 --> 00:20:32,950
feel free to bring the painting from Shuiyun Theater here.

396
00:20:33,180 --> 00:20:34,490
Take a look for yourself.

397
00:20:35,000 --> 00:20:35,530
Right…

398
00:20:36,570 --> 00:20:39,310
You little bastard with no mentor and respect.

399
00:20:41,210 --> 00:20:43,620
You father would’ve called me his senior.

400
00:20:43,630 --> 00:20:45,940
There’s no way I’m blaming the wrong person.

401
00:20:48,120 --> 00:20:48,720
If I don’t

402
00:20:48,730 --> 00:20:50,400
teach you a lesson today

403
00:20:50,410 --> 00:20:52,270
and regulate the opera industry,

404
00:20:52,460 --> 00:20:54,830
I will die with shame!

405
00:21:02,220 --> 00:21:02,910
Where are you going?

406
00:21:03,160 --> 00:21:04,580
The leader hasn’t come back for so long.

407
00:21:04,590 --> 00:21:06,230
He must have been kept by them there.

408
00:21:06,240 --> 00:21:08,070
Mr. Du and Mr. Niu are both scholars.

409
00:21:08,080 --> 00:21:09,270
They’re too polite for that occasion.

410
00:21:09,280 --> 00:21:10,070
I need to go help them.

411
00:21:10,080 --> 00:21:11,240
What kind of help would you be?

412
00:21:11,250 --> 00:21:11,950
All they need is to talk it over.

413
00:21:11,960 --> 00:21:13,010
It’s not a fight scene!

414
00:21:14,410 --> 00:21:15,040
Mr. Du!

415
00:21:15,050 --> 00:21:16,090
Mr. Du. Mr. Du.

416
00:21:16,100 --> 00:21:16,690
What happened?

417
00:21:16,700 --> 00:21:17,300
Hurry up,

418
00:21:17,310 --> 00:21:18,230
go to the Association.

419
00:21:18,240 --> 00:21:19,290
Your leader is in trouble.

420
00:21:19,750 --> 00:21:20,320
What?

421
00:21:20,650 --> 00:21:22,490
How are you back here alone?

422
00:21:22,700 --> 00:21:23,580
My father is ill.

423
00:21:23,750 --> 00:21:24,610
I need to go back.

424
00:21:24,620 --> 00:21:26,120
Just to let you know on my way back.

425
00:21:26,660 --> 00:21:27,370
Thank you, Mr. Du.

426
00:21:27,380 --> 00:21:29,960
This bastard. He’s really going to hurt him.

427
00:21:29,970 --> 00:21:31,400
It’s hard to say now.

428
00:21:31,830 --> 00:21:32,870
But it’s not going well.

429
00:21:33,080 --> 00:21:33,700
Hurry up.

430
00:21:33,880 --> 00:21:35,270
Don’t let them bully him.

431
00:21:35,400 --> 00:21:37,420
Take your weapons! Let’s go!

432
00:21:37,430 --> 00:21:38,270
Are you insane?

433
00:21:38,280 --> 00:21:39,710
-Are you seriously going to fight there? -Let’s go!

434
00:21:39,720 --> 00:21:40,880
We’ll never be able to perform in Peking anymore!

435
00:21:40,890 --> 00:21:41,920
Dasheng, stop right there!

436
00:21:41,930 --> 00:21:43,100
- Everyone stop! - Hey!

437
00:21:43,480 --> 00:21:45,550
Jiang Rongshou took the opportunity.

438
00:21:45,670 --> 00:21:47,630
He started this

439
00:21:47,640 --> 00:21:49,200
right after Mr. Cheng left.

440
00:21:49,700 --> 00:21:51,000
Such a bully.

441
00:21:51,130 --> 00:21:53,200
If we toughen up, he’ll be such a coward.

442
00:21:53,570 --> 00:21:54,130
Exactly!

443
00:21:54,890 --> 00:21:55,970
From what I see,

444
00:21:56,170 --> 00:21:58,790
he’s merely the head of the Association.

445
00:21:58,800 --> 00:22:00,380
Does he think he’s a mafia head or what?

446
00:22:00,880 --> 00:22:02,820
We should go protect our leader

447
00:22:02,830 --> 00:22:04,280
and teach them a lesson!

448
00:22:04,290 --> 00:22:04,750
Let’s go!

449
00:22:04,760 --> 00:22:06,080
No one can bully our leader!

450
00:22:06,090 --> 00:22:06,770
Let’s go!

451
00:22:07,320 --> 00:22:08,020
- Come on! - Dasheng!

452
00:22:08,030 --> 00:22:08,800
Hit them hard!

453
00:22:08,810 --> 00:22:09,850
You bet, Mr. Du!

454
00:22:11,640 --> 00:22:13,160
Here at the Association,

455
00:22:13,320 --> 00:22:16,020
we perform to educate people.

456
00:22:16,420 --> 00:22:18,050
Zhao Feiyan schemed to kill the prince,

457
00:22:18,060 --> 00:22:19,160
making a mess in the palace.

458
00:22:19,170 --> 00:22:21,110
What’s the last scene in your script?

459
00:22:21,380 --> 00:22:24,880
Zhao Feiyan became the queen.

460
00:22:25,890 --> 00:22:28,520
Your fans sit in your theater the entire night.

461
00:22:28,530 --> 00:22:29,610
What do they want to see?

462
00:22:31,380 --> 00:22:33,850
They want to see justice.

463
00:22:33,860 --> 00:22:35,710
They want to see karma.

464
00:22:37,090 --> 00:22:38,330
But in your show,

465
00:22:39,180 --> 00:22:41,620
the villain gets her happy ending.

466
00:22:43,830 --> 00:22:45,380
What would your audience think?

467
00:22:47,660 --> 00:22:50,330
Are they going to kill and abandon their wives as well?

468
00:22:50,340 --> 00:22:52,320
Zhao Feiyan died eventually.

469
00:22:52,520 --> 00:22:54,030
How is that a happy ending for her?

470
00:22:55,450 --> 00:22:57,230
Then why don’t you show that in your script?

471
00:22:57,240 --> 00:22:58,140
I can’t.

472
00:22:59,020 --> 00:23:00,060
Mr. Du said

473
00:23:00,710 --> 00:23:02,930
there are only 3 hours for a show.

474
00:23:02,940 --> 00:23:04,750
Not enough time for every plot.

475
00:23:05,030 --> 00:23:06,630
The protagonist was 80 years old.

476
00:23:06,640 --> 00:23:07,740
It wouldn’t be a good show.

477
00:23:08,190 --> 00:23:09,840
Mr. Du said?

478
00:23:11,000 --> 00:23:12,350
He has no right.

479
00:23:12,360 --> 00:23:14,860
I’m here to teach you a lesson today.

480
00:23:15,790 --> 00:23:18,040
You’re Zhang Beidou’s student.

481
00:23:18,210 --> 00:23:20,560
You don’t discuss your show with your peers.

482
00:23:20,840 --> 00:23:22,660
But you’d listen to an outsider.

483
00:23:22,670 --> 00:23:24,100
What a disgrace!

484
00:23:25,800 --> 00:23:26,420
What’s more,

485
00:23:27,230 --> 00:23:29,090
you discarded the old system.

486
00:23:29,540 --> 00:23:32,230
And started this so-called contract system.

487
00:23:32,510 --> 00:23:33,600
You’re throwing away our tradition

488
00:23:33,610 --> 00:23:35,970
of hundreds of years.

489
00:23:37,100 --> 00:23:38,590
This is disrespecting your ancestors.

490
00:23:38,600 --> 00:23:40,610
The contract system is better than the old one.

491
00:23:41,700 --> 00:23:42,610
What did you just say?

492
00:23:42,620 --> 00:23:45,260
The contract system is better than the old one.

493
00:23:46,160 --> 00:23:46,950
The contract system

494
00:23:47,590 --> 00:23:49,020
is about human rights.

495
00:23:49,720 --> 00:23:51,660
The old system turned someone into an object.

496
00:23:51,670 --> 00:23:53,020
No one should belong to a theater

497
00:23:53,030 --> 00:23:55,790
for the rest of his life.

498
00:23:59,430 --> 00:24:00,400
You all heard it.

499
00:24:01,660 --> 00:24:04,540
You also think the contract system is better?

500
00:24:04,550 --> 00:24:06,040
This… Well…

501
00:24:06,610 --> 00:24:07,640
Contract…

502
00:24:10,000 --> 00:24:11,300
Gentlemen.

503
00:24:11,310 --> 00:24:12,010
Gentlemen.

504
00:24:12,220 --> 00:24:13,590
Allow me to jump in.

505
00:24:13,600 --> 00:24:14,410
Let me say this.

506
00:24:14,770 --> 00:24:16,080
I believe

507
00:24:16,920 --> 00:24:17,610
we should just

508
00:24:17,940 --> 00:24:20,320
take care of our own business.

509
00:24:20,800 --> 00:24:22,880
Mr. Shang can use his contract system.

510
00:24:23,120 --> 00:24:24,020
And you can keep using

511
00:24:24,030 --> 00:24:25,520
your old system.

512
00:24:25,750 --> 00:24:27,640
Win-win. Right?

513
00:24:27,650 --> 00:24:28,320
Mr. Niu.

514
00:24:29,360 --> 00:24:30,720
I beg to disagree.

515
00:24:32,690 --> 00:24:33,790
I have to say.

516
00:24:37,490 --> 00:24:39,460
Mr. Shang. You’re better than us.

517
00:24:40,410 --> 00:24:42,460
You can burn the life-time indenture.

518
00:24:43,270 --> 00:24:45,820
There will be countless people who will help you.

519
00:24:46,050 --> 00:24:47,340
But we’re different.

520
00:24:47,590 --> 00:24:48,910
Lots of parents

521
00:24:48,920 --> 00:24:51,560
heard that we’re using this contract system.

522
00:24:52,120 --> 00:24:54,420
They wouldn’t sell their children to us.

523
00:24:56,460 --> 00:24:57,920
Some even wanted to take their children back.

524
00:24:59,280 --> 00:25:00,640
You can ask them.

525
00:25:01,810 --> 00:25:02,670
If they all do this,

526
00:25:03,820 --> 00:25:04,930
there won’t be any business for us anymore.

527
00:25:05,340 --> 00:25:05,730
Right!

528
00:25:06,440 --> 00:25:07,440
The old tradition

529
00:25:07,450 --> 00:25:08,890
was created by our ancestors.

530
00:25:08,900 --> 00:25:09,560
You can’t change it.

531
00:25:09,710 --> 00:25:10,880
Without this tradition,

532
00:25:10,890 --> 00:25:12,460
these kids will leave after they learned everything.

533
00:25:12,600 --> 00:25:14,070
It’d be a great loss for us.

534
00:25:14,080 --> 00:25:14,720
Exactly.

535
00:25:14,940 --> 00:25:16,760
Two systems in one industry.

536
00:25:16,770 --> 00:25:17,500
This is not appropriate.

537
00:25:17,510 --> 00:25:18,550
If you continue like this,

538
00:25:18,560 --> 00:25:20,550
there won’t be a future for us.

539
00:25:20,680 --> 00:25:21,670
Right, everyone?

540
00:25:21,680 --> 00:25:23,080
That’s right. Yes.

541
00:25:23,090 --> 00:25:24,830
Look at it. Look at it.

542
00:25:24,840 --> 00:25:25,780
Shang Xirui,

543
00:25:26,060 --> 00:25:27,880
you’ve upset people.

544
00:25:27,890 --> 00:25:29,270
I stand with what I said.

545
00:25:30,450 --> 00:25:33,470
Contract system is better.

546
00:25:34,100 --> 00:25:36,270
We’re all artists and performers.

547
00:25:36,690 --> 00:25:39,270
If we don’t respect each other,

548
00:25:39,280 --> 00:25:40,840
who will?

549
00:25:41,590 --> 00:25:43,390
You sell animals. Not people.

550
00:25:43,400 --> 00:25:44,320
What are you talking about?

551
00:25:46,200 --> 00:25:47,990
Who are you lecturing

552
00:25:48,000 --> 00:25:49,400
in front of our grandmaster?

553
00:25:49,560 --> 00:25:50,110
Gentlemen,

554
00:25:51,330 --> 00:25:53,480
please take my advice.

555
00:25:54,790 --> 00:25:55,490
If someone stays

556
00:25:56,970 --> 00:25:59,260
because he belongs to you,

557
00:26:00,550 --> 00:26:02,600
even if he’s physically there,

558
00:26:03,250 --> 00:26:05,750
he’s not with you emotionally.

559
00:26:06,170 --> 00:26:07,350
It’s just like in the play.

560
00:26:07,700 --> 00:26:10,200
Why did Pan Jinlian kill Wu Dalang?

561
00:26:10,210 --> 00:26:11,950
Because she was cheating on him.

562
00:26:12,160 --> 00:26:13,190
She couldn’t leave

563
00:26:13,390 --> 00:26:14,720
even if she wanted to.

564
00:26:14,730 --> 00:26:16,350
Eventually she had no choice.

565
00:26:16,360 --> 00:26:17,440
That’s how the tragedy happened.

566
00:26:18,930 --> 00:26:20,530
If this was consensual

567
00:26:20,980 --> 00:26:22,650
from the beginning,

568
00:26:22,660 --> 00:26:23,810
if she had the option,

569
00:26:24,340 --> 00:26:25,680
he wouldn’t have died.

570
00:26:27,040 --> 00:26:29,350
What kind of nonsense is this?

571
00:26:29,360 --> 00:26:30,550
Who is Pan Jinlian?

572
00:26:31,010 --> 00:26:32,620
Who is Wu Dalang?

573
00:26:32,630 --> 00:26:34,840
I have heard that Mr. Shang

574
00:26:34,850 --> 00:26:36,790
does things differently.

575
00:26:38,160 --> 00:26:39,700
But today,

576
00:26:41,180 --> 00:26:42,790
I finally saw it for myself.

577
00:26:44,680 --> 00:26:45,440
Sir,

578
00:26:46,140 --> 00:26:47,440
we insist,

579
00:26:47,960 --> 00:26:49,360
you have to teach him a lesson today.

580
00:26:50,180 --> 00:26:50,520
We insist!

581
00:26:50,530 --> 00:26:51,580
Gentlemen. Gentlemen.

582
00:26:51,590 --> 00:26:53,190
Relax. Relax.

583
00:26:54,000 --> 00:26:55,830
This disrespectful bastard.

584
00:26:55,840 --> 00:26:56,400
Anyone else

585
00:26:56,410 --> 00:26:58,180
wants to help him?

586
00:27:00,200 --> 00:27:01,950
Alright, Shang Xirui.

587
00:27:04,090 --> 00:27:06,790
I’ll forgive you

588
00:27:06,800 --> 00:27:08,550
for that you lost your father young.

589
00:27:09,790 --> 00:27:11,040
You should probably kneel down

590
00:27:11,460 --> 00:27:14,400
and kowtow for your grandmaster.

591
00:27:14,410 --> 00:27:15,240
And apologise.

592
00:27:15,610 --> 00:27:17,490
If I do,

593
00:27:18,890 --> 00:27:22,230
I’d be this traitor who disrespected my master.

594
00:27:24,200 --> 00:27:25,090
I didn’t do anything wrong!

595
00:27:26,080 --> 00:27:26,760
Somebody!

596
00:27:28,440 --> 00:27:28,910
Mr. Shang,

597
00:27:28,920 --> 00:27:30,580
just do as he says.

598
00:27:30,810 --> 00:27:32,500
Make him kneel!

599
00:27:32,510 --> 00:27:34,180
Make him apologise

600
00:27:34,190 --> 00:27:35,380
to our grandmaster!

601
00:27:35,390 --> 00:27:35,940
Sir!

602
00:27:35,950 --> 00:27:37,150
Please. Please don’t.

603
00:27:37,160 --> 00:27:38,680
Get out. This is none of your business.

604
00:27:39,850 --> 00:27:40,720
I dare you!

605
00:27:44,840 --> 00:27:45,760
Whoever comes near me,

606
00:27:47,960 --> 00:27:49,280
I won’t go easy on you.

607
00:27:53,150 --> 00:27:53,840
Put him down.

608
00:27:55,350 --> 00:27:57,820
Any problem, I’ll take care of it.

609
00:27:58,690 --> 00:27:59,380
Hit him!

610
00:28:34,500 --> 00:28:35,820
What’s happening?

611
00:28:39,430 --> 00:28:40,370
Out of the way!

612
00:28:42,500 --> 00:28:43,400
They’re from Shuiyun Theater.

613
00:28:46,510 --> 00:28:47,770
Can’t see anything.

614
00:28:47,780 --> 00:28:49,360
I don’t care. Let’s go!

615
00:28:49,370 --> 00:28:49,920
- Let’s go! - No!

616
00:28:49,930 --> 00:28:50,780
Out of my way!

617
00:28:51,220 --> 00:28:53,030
Leader! Leader!

618
00:28:53,040 --> 00:28:53,940
Don’t you dare!

619
00:28:53,950 --> 00:28:54,750
Stop it now!

620
00:28:56,400 --> 00:28:57,730
Shang Xirui!

621
00:29:02,180 --> 00:29:03,630
If you leave now,

622
00:29:03,640 --> 00:29:05,230
you will never come back again!

623
00:29:10,400 --> 00:29:11,250
This door

624
00:29:11,760 --> 00:29:12,990
is like a death trap.

625
00:29:13,590 --> 00:29:14,560
I don’t care about coming back.

626
00:29:15,470 --> 00:29:16,560
Great.

627
00:29:16,890 --> 00:29:18,110
You said it.

628
00:29:18,450 --> 00:29:19,040
Dengbao,

629
00:29:19,050 --> 00:29:20,550
get me the name book.

630
00:29:20,920 --> 00:29:22,390
Sir, calm down.

631
00:29:22,560 --> 00:29:22,990
Dad.

632
00:29:23,660 --> 00:29:25,280
I will be the one to kick him out

633
00:29:26,040 --> 00:29:30,520
for our grandmaster today.

634
00:29:30,530 --> 00:29:31,460
Sir…

635
00:29:39,780 --> 00:29:41,300
(Fifth Generation: Shang Xirui)

636
00:29:49,550 --> 00:29:50,190
Leader.

637
00:29:56,660 --> 00:29:58,210
My talent is with me.

638
00:29:58,490 --> 00:30:00,380
Not with that piece of paper.

639
00:30:01,500 --> 00:30:02,610
Leader. Leader.

640
00:30:02,620 --> 00:30:04,190
Remember what you said.

641
00:30:04,910 --> 00:30:06,590
Don’t come back!

642
00:30:16,850 --> 00:30:17,900
Sir!

643
00:30:19,460 --> 00:30:20,120
Boss,

644
00:30:20,130 --> 00:30:21,040
Erjiebao ran away!

645
00:30:21,410 --> 00:30:23,070
Alright. Alright. That’s fine.

646
00:30:23,570 --> 00:30:24,880
If anyone finds him again,

647
00:30:24,890 --> 00:30:25,810
kill him.

648
00:30:27,870 --> 00:30:29,140
Whoever kills him,

649
00:30:29,280 --> 00:30:31,650
I’ll reward him 500 dollars.

650
00:30:31,660 --> 00:30:36,180
Yes. Yes!

651
00:30:36,780 --> 00:30:38,120
Please, Mr. Cheng.

652
00:30:55,090 --> 00:30:56,020
Mr. Cheng.

653
00:30:56,810 --> 00:30:58,470
We haven’t met for 7 or 8 years.

654
00:30:59,010 --> 00:31:00,560
You didn’t change.

655
00:31:02,640 --> 00:31:04,600
Dali, you’ve changed, though.

656
00:31:05,380 --> 00:31:07,520
When I passed Laozi Ridge back then,

657
00:31:07,650 --> 00:31:09,660
you were just a little girl.

658
00:31:12,450 --> 00:31:13,750
She’s a girl?

659
00:31:14,690 --> 00:31:16,730
She’s more like a savage…

660
00:31:18,880 --> 00:31:20,230
What do you think

661
00:31:20,240 --> 00:31:21,520
I should look like then?

662
00:31:25,080 --> 00:31:25,920
Well.

663
00:31:26,970 --> 00:31:29,090
You have the spirit of your father.

664
00:31:29,650 --> 00:31:31,340
You’re also very talented

665
00:31:31,350 --> 00:31:33,120
leading your troop.

666
00:31:33,720 --> 00:31:34,990
You’re indeed

667
00:31:36,100 --> 00:31:37,120
a heroine.

668
00:31:38,700 --> 00:31:39,660
Absolutely.

669
00:31:40,550 --> 00:31:42,040
My dad was excellent.

670
00:31:42,600 --> 00:31:43,710
I am his daughter.

671
00:31:43,720 --> 00:31:44,920
I can’t be too lame.

672
00:31:45,160 --> 00:31:45,740
Indeed.

673
00:31:46,990 --> 00:31:49,940
Thank you Dali for saving us.

674
00:31:50,250 --> 00:31:52,550
Saving me and my silly brother

675
00:31:52,560 --> 00:31:53,330
from hell.

676
00:31:58,620 --> 00:31:59,450
As a matter of fact,

677
00:32:00,490 --> 00:32:01,610
I felt very sad

678
00:32:02,620 --> 00:32:04,320
when your father left.

679
00:32:05,400 --> 00:32:06,550
When I get back this time,

680
00:32:07,200 --> 00:32:08,780
I will hold a ceremony for him.

681
00:32:09,120 --> 00:32:10,450
To bring you more peace.

682
00:32:11,240 --> 00:32:12,140
You can’t leave yet.

683
00:32:13,160 --> 00:32:15,000
I haven’t granted you to leave.

684
00:32:15,610 --> 00:32:17,720
We need to talk about our problems.

685
00:32:18,400 --> 00:32:19,030
Please.

686
00:32:26,880 --> 00:32:28,440
What is it that you’d like to talk about?

687
00:32:29,730 --> 00:32:30,610
My dad died.

688
00:32:31,240 --> 00:32:33,100
I’m now the new boss here at Laozi Ridge.

689
00:32:34,680 --> 00:32:36,130
So I’m resetting

690
00:32:36,350 --> 00:32:37,530
the rules here.

691
00:32:38,800 --> 00:32:40,080
Whoever passes by,

692
00:32:40,200 --> 00:32:41,120
will have to pay.

693
00:32:41,920 --> 00:32:43,270
From now on,

694
00:32:44,120 --> 00:32:45,760
you will pay 20% more.

695
00:32:48,670 --> 00:32:49,920
20% more?

696
00:32:54,180 --> 00:32:55,420
There won’t be anything left to me.

697
00:32:57,020 --> 00:32:59,170
You make a lot of money

698
00:32:59,180 --> 00:33:00,490
because of my dad’s help.

699
00:33:00,500 --> 00:33:03,380
He protected you from all your competitors.

700
00:33:03,900 --> 00:33:05,520
20% is nothing.

701
00:33:06,470 --> 00:33:08,120
You should do it anyway.

702
00:33:10,570 --> 00:33:12,680
You said your father protected me.

703
00:33:13,370 --> 00:33:14,430
Indeed.

704
00:33:15,230 --> 00:33:16,720
But why did he

705
00:33:17,280 --> 00:33:20,130
only protect me?

706
00:33:20,760 --> 00:33:21,660
Why didn’t he protect all the others

707
00:33:21,670 --> 00:33:23,410
from the Peking Chamber of Commerce?

708
00:33:24,660 --> 00:33:26,260
That’s because I was generous.

709
00:33:26,670 --> 00:33:28,550
I fed him well.

710
00:33:29,740 --> 00:33:30,490
Sister,

711
00:33:31,130 --> 00:33:33,080
why don’t you go back and go through his record?

712
00:33:33,520 --> 00:33:35,000
And we can talk later.

713
00:33:35,900 --> 00:33:36,550
Bullshit!

714
00:33:37,360 --> 00:33:39,120
I said 20%. So it will be 20%.

715
00:33:47,220 --> 00:33:48,690
This is not to be negotiated.

716
00:33:51,680 --> 00:33:54,700
You’re asking for whatever you want.

717
00:33:55,360 --> 00:33:57,850
Do whatever you do to me.

718
00:33:58,520 --> 00:33:59,480
But you won’t get a dime from me.

719
00:34:00,650 --> 00:34:01,940
Go ahead.

720
00:34:03,130 --> 00:34:04,440
Bro… Brother…

721
00:34:04,730 --> 00:34:05,940
Let’s give her what she wants.

722
00:34:06,580 --> 00:34:07,960
Your life is more important.

723
00:34:09,159 --> 00:34:10,659
You businessmen

724
00:34:10,670 --> 00:34:12,440
really value money over life.

725
00:34:14,420 --> 00:34:15,610
I’m not only going to kill you

726
00:34:15,960 --> 00:34:17,300
and your men.

727
00:34:17,840 --> 00:34:19,070
I’m also going to kill your brother-in-law.

728
00:34:19,630 --> 00:34:21,670
No one leaves alive.

729
00:34:21,679 --> 00:34:22,760
Whatever.

730
00:34:23,250 --> 00:34:24,550
I can’t care about them less

731
00:34:24,889 --> 00:34:26,850
since I’m dying anyway.

732
00:34:29,400 --> 00:34:30,260
Great.

733
00:34:32,219 --> 00:34:33,560
As you wish.

734
00:34:35,199 --> 00:34:36,600
Brother… Bro… Brother…

735
00:34:37,080 --> 00:34:37,790
Take them out!

736
00:34:39,540 --> 00:34:40,500
Don’t touch me.

737
00:34:40,989 --> 00:34:42,159
I can walk on my own.

738
00:34:42,880 --> 00:34:43,400
What…

739
00:34:44,460 --> 00:34:45,949
Brother… Brother!

740
00:34:46,179 --> 00:34:48,130
Let’s talk about this, shall we?

741
00:34:48,860 --> 00:34:49,760
On your knees!

742
00:34:49,900 --> 00:34:51,040
Don’t touch me.

743
00:34:53,800 --> 00:34:55,750
I see you’ve had enough of your life.

744
00:34:57,700 --> 00:34:58,810
Wait, this thing hurts.

745
00:34:59,230 --> 00:35:01,180
I gave your father so many guns and bombs.

746
00:35:01,400 --> 00:35:02,480
Would you be so generous

747
00:35:02,760 --> 00:35:03,880
and bless me with a bullet?

748
00:35:05,500 --> 00:35:06,240
Fine.

749
00:35:09,360 --> 00:35:10,560
As you wish!

750
00:35:12,160 --> 00:35:12,740
Wait a second.

751
00:35:13,930 --> 00:35:15,080
Take off his clothes.

752
00:35:15,720 --> 00:35:16,630
That’s some really nice mink fur.

753
00:35:16,640 --> 00:35:18,660
Would be a shame to ruin it.

754
00:35:28,460 --> 00:35:29,860
Let me ask you again.

755
00:35:30,320 --> 00:35:31,520
20% more.

756
00:35:32,060 --> 00:35:33,080
Yes or no?

757
00:35:34,930 --> 00:35:35,970
No.

758
00:36:02,600 --> 00:36:03,320
Sister,

759
00:36:04,160 --> 00:36:05,840
where are you going? It’s so late.

760
00:36:08,520 --> 00:36:10,180
Mr. Huang is playing poker tonight.

761
00:36:10,340 --> 00:36:11,850
They invited me over.

762
00:36:12,840 --> 00:36:15,280
Didn’t Mr. Huang and his family go back to Anhui?

763
00:36:15,470 --> 00:36:16,830
How are they playing poker here?

764
00:36:18,760 --> 00:36:20,360
Well, they’re indeed leaving.

765
00:36:20,640 --> 00:36:21,760
That’s why they want to meet up.

766
00:36:23,720 --> 00:36:25,000
Sister, don’t lie to me.

767
00:36:26,470 --> 00:36:27,520
Tell me,

768
00:36:28,280 --> 00:36:29,490
did anything happen to Mr. Cheng?

769
00:36:30,520 --> 00:36:32,400
What could possibly happen to him?

770
00:36:33,600 --> 00:36:35,510
He left in a hurry last time.

771
00:36:35,920 --> 00:36:37,450
Said that he wanted to check out some cargos there.

772
00:36:37,460 --> 00:36:39,040
That was all he said.

773
00:36:40,250 --> 00:36:40,760
I know him.

774
00:36:40,770 --> 00:36:43,010
The more dangerous it is, the less he tells me.

775
00:36:43,430 --> 00:36:44,860
He doesn’t want to worry me.

776
00:36:45,890 --> 00:36:47,520
I usually just let it slide.

777
00:36:48,300 --> 00:36:49,790
But if anything really happened to him,

778
00:36:49,800 --> 00:36:50,490
sister,

779
00:36:50,640 --> 00:36:52,090
don’t hide it away from me for him.

780
00:36:58,170 --> 00:36:59,440
Things happened at Laozi Ridge.

781
00:37:01,400 --> 00:37:02,540
The previous chief died.

782
00:37:03,120 --> 00:37:05,490
The one under him captured Fan Lian.

783
00:37:07,570 --> 00:37:08,340
And then,

784
00:37:08,640 --> 00:37:10,090
brother went to save him.

785
00:37:12,320 --> 00:37:13,820
What… what about now?

786
00:37:14,360 --> 00:37:15,480
I don’t know.

787
00:37:19,240 --> 00:37:21,250
My family had dealt with bandits before.

788
00:37:21,760 --> 00:37:24,130
I can ask them to talk to those people.

789
00:37:24,450 --> 00:37:26,280
Your family does business.

790
00:37:26,880 --> 00:37:28,810
Businessmen can’t just go in there.

791
00:37:28,820 --> 00:37:31,100
They will take you down all at once.

792
00:37:33,060 --> 00:37:34,340
They are bandits.

793
00:37:34,960 --> 00:37:36,250
Bullets work best on them.

794
00:37:38,450 --> 00:37:39,640
I’ll take care of it.

795
00:37:43,660 --> 00:37:44,450
Sister,

796
00:37:46,240 --> 00:37:49,180
my brother always praises you.

797
00:37:49,750 --> 00:37:50,660
You marrying him

798
00:37:50,670 --> 00:37:52,220
is like a big fish in a small pond.

799
00:37:52,980 --> 00:37:54,600
He’s been away for too long this time.

800
00:37:54,900 --> 00:37:56,970
The Chamber of Commerce might come.

801
00:37:57,600 --> 00:38:00,350
Please take care of our business at home.

802
00:38:01,880 --> 00:38:02,790
Don’t you worry, sister.

803
00:38:03,750 --> 00:38:05,410
I will take care of it.

804
00:38:07,920 --> 00:38:09,000
When he comes back,

805
00:38:09,440 --> 00:38:10,710
I’ll make sure he thanks you.

806
00:38:11,460 --> 00:38:13,060
We’re husband and wife. There’s no need.

807
00:38:14,520 --> 00:38:15,550
It’s really dark out there.

808
00:38:15,560 --> 00:38:16,480
Do be careful.

809
00:38:16,800 --> 00:38:17,360
Alright.

810
00:38:18,130 --> 00:38:18,860
I’ll get going then.

811
00:38:26,960 --> 00:38:28,590
Keep the light on tonight. Don’t turn it off.

812
00:38:29,260 --> 00:38:30,590
Let’s keep it bright.

813
00:38:31,460 --> 00:38:32,330
I’ll do it now.

814
00:38:40,410 --> 00:38:43,200
Mr. Cheng is captured at Laozi Ridge?

815
00:38:46,240 --> 00:38:47,690
Didn’t know the words got out so fast.

816
00:38:50,250 --> 00:38:52,150
Lots of gun shots at the Laozi Ridge.

817
00:38:52,160 --> 00:38:54,380
People can see it from miles away.

818
00:38:55,120 --> 00:38:56,710
I also know that

819
00:38:56,720 --> 00:38:58,040
he left for the east side a few days ago.

820
00:39:01,420 --> 00:39:02,240
Sir,

821
00:39:03,690 --> 00:39:05,880
you know about my brother’s plan so well.

822
00:39:06,620 --> 00:39:07,980
What are you planning to do?

823
00:39:09,600 --> 00:39:11,150
What I’m planning to do

824
00:39:11,940 --> 00:39:12,840
doesn’t really matter.

825
00:39:13,530 --> 00:39:14,910
What matters is

826
00:39:14,920 --> 00:39:18,230
his life.

827
00:39:20,280 --> 00:39:20,890
Fine.

828
00:39:22,540 --> 00:39:23,880
Then I kindly ask you

829
00:39:24,570 --> 00:39:26,060
to save his life.

830
00:39:28,520 --> 00:39:30,460
Asking me to send my people to save him?

831
00:39:32,610 --> 00:39:34,250
The commander left for Nanjing already.

832
00:39:34,450 --> 00:39:36,420
You’re in charge of the soldiers here at the house of Cao.

833
00:39:37,090 --> 00:39:38,880
Of course I’m asking you to help.

834
00:39:44,920 --> 00:39:46,480
You only think of me

835
00:39:46,660 --> 00:39:47,960
when the commander is away.

836
00:39:51,490 --> 00:39:52,960
How is that I’m always

837
00:39:53,750 --> 00:39:55,560
not as important as he is?

838
00:40:00,220 --> 00:40:01,900
If you save Fengtai this time,

839
00:40:03,360 --> 00:40:05,510
it’d be the best chance to befriend him.

840
00:40:06,640 --> 00:40:07,290
I know

841
00:40:08,380 --> 00:40:09,540
that you want something from him.

842
00:40:21,700 --> 00:40:24,960
I want a lot from him.

843
00:40:29,440 --> 00:40:31,000
As long as he comes home in one piece,

844
00:40:31,820 --> 00:40:33,000
I can assure you,

845
00:40:33,770 --> 00:40:35,610
I will make sure he works with you.

846
00:40:41,680 --> 00:40:42,960
Will he listen to you?

847
00:40:50,540 --> 00:40:51,450
What do you think?

848
00:40:55,120 --> 00:40:57,960
When was the last time someone rejected you?

849
00:41:03,820 --> 00:41:05,780
You never had a hard time,

850
00:41:06,510 --> 00:41:07,650
being so clever

851
00:41:07,660 --> 00:41:09,000
and so pretty.

852
00:41:10,090 --> 00:41:13,180
Even when your parents passed away,

853
00:41:13,630 --> 00:41:15,200
no one has ever said no to you

854
00:41:15,670 --> 00:41:19,470
because of your charm.

855
00:41:28,100 --> 00:41:28,840
So?

856
00:41:31,040 --> 00:41:32,450
Are you going to reject me today?

857
00:41:41,600 --> 00:41:42,260
Ma’am,

858
00:41:43,790 --> 00:41:44,800
go home and wait for the news.

859
00:41:47,880 --> 00:41:48,800
That adjutant… What’s his name?

860
00:41:51,080 --> 00:41:51,880
Adjutant Sun!

861
00:41:52,300 --> 00:41:53,250
Get your people!

862
00:41:53,840 --> 00:41:54,580
Follow me!

863
00:42:38,200 --> 00:42:39,530
What on earth are you doing?

864
00:42:40,160 --> 00:42:40,720
Get down.

865
00:42:42,850 --> 00:42:43,950
Eat.

866
00:42:43,960 --> 00:42:45,240
No thanks. Don’t want to.

867
00:42:45,250 --> 00:42:45,610
You…

868
00:42:47,050 --> 00:42:49,000
Don’t want to? Don’t be silly.

869
00:42:49,810 --> 00:42:50,710
You have nothing in your belly.

870
00:42:50,720 --> 00:42:52,060
How are you going to practice properly?

871
00:42:52,210 --> 00:42:52,900
Don’t mind me.

872
00:42:53,340 --> 00:42:54,200
I’m working out.

873
00:42:54,340 --> 00:42:55,200
I’ll start tumbling later.

874
00:42:55,620 --> 00:42:55,970
You…

875
00:42:56,280 --> 00:42:58,000
Who tumbles indoor?

876
00:42:58,010 --> 00:42:58,800
Do it outside.

877
00:43:04,420 --> 00:43:05,020
Fine.

878
00:43:05,740 --> 00:43:07,670
Let’s see how long you can hang in here.

879
00:43:17,110 --> 00:43:18,160
Interesting.

880
00:43:18,430 --> 00:43:20,630
Never knew there’d be a day when he can’t eat.

881
00:43:21,560 --> 00:43:23,190
I don’t see him being injured horribly.

882
00:43:23,480 --> 00:43:24,830
Just some scratches.

883
00:43:25,140 --> 00:43:27,140
Physically, no.

884
00:43:27,150 --> 00:43:29,420
But the rumors and people talking behind his back…

885
00:43:29,430 --> 00:43:31,140
And those nonsense on the newspaper.

886
00:43:31,330 --> 00:43:32,890
Jiang Rongshou is clever.

887
00:43:34,880 --> 00:43:37,980
He knew that our leader is impulsive.

888
00:43:37,990 --> 00:43:39,430
He accused him of so many things

889
00:43:39,440 --> 00:43:41,020
in front of so many people.

890
00:43:42,080 --> 00:43:44,720
If our leader apologised,

891
00:43:45,040 --> 00:43:46,740
then he’ll be the boss from now on.

892
00:43:47,280 --> 00:43:47,880
But,

893
00:43:47,890 --> 00:43:49,530
if our leader got physical,

894
00:43:49,540 --> 00:43:50,700
that’s even better.

895
00:43:51,140 --> 00:43:53,990
Our leader would become the traitor in this industry.

896
00:43:55,490 --> 00:43:57,120
Our leader is always too straight forward.

897
00:43:57,410 --> 00:43:58,600
Anyone pisses him off,

898
00:43:58,790 --> 00:43:59,840
he easily gets physical.

899
00:44:00,210 --> 00:44:02,380
His personality is a ticking time bomb.

900
00:44:03,080 --> 00:44:04,230
Mr. Cheng is away now.

901
00:44:04,240 --> 00:44:05,680
No one here to guide us.

902
00:44:06,390 --> 00:44:07,540
Don’t even mention him.

903
00:44:07,860 --> 00:44:09,090
Can’t find him anywhere.

904
00:44:09,270 --> 00:44:10,570
What do you think he can do?

905
00:44:14,010 --> 00:44:15,780
How’s everything, ladies and gentlemen?

906
00:44:16,740 --> 00:44:17,710
Is Mr. Shang here?
